InstanceOf(classOf[SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage])\n    assertThat(restored.asInstanceOf[SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage].payload())\n      .containsExactly(GeneratedMessageLiteInnerSerializedFormTest.LegacyPayload*)\n  }\n\n  private def serializeFormAndReadBackWithClassNameLookup(message: MessageLite): AnyRef = {\n    val bytes: ByteArrayOutputStream = new ByteArrayOutputStream()\n    Using.resource(new SerializedFormClassNullingObjectOutputStream(bytes)) { output =>\n      output.writeObject(GeneratedMessageLite.SerializedForm.of(message))\n    }\n\n    Using.resource(new ObjectInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(bytes.toByteArray))) { input =>\n      input.readObject()\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nobject GeneratedMessageLiteInnerSerializedFormTest {\n  private val ModernPayload: Array[Byte] = Array[Byte](1, 3, 5, 7)\n  private val LegacyPayload: Array[Byte] = Array[Byte](2, 4, 6, 8)\n}\n\nclass SerializedFormClassNullingObjectOutputStream(output: OutputStream) extends ObjectOutputStream(output) {\n  enableReplaceObject(true)\n\n  override protected def replaceObject(obj: AnyRef): AnyRef = {\n    if (obj == classOf[SerializedFormModernLiteMessage] || obj == classOf[SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage]) {\n      null\n    } else {\n      super.replaceObject(obj)\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nabstract class SerializedFormBaseLiteMessage(private val bytes: Array[Byte]) extends MessageLite {\n  def payload(): Array[Byte] = Arrays.copyOf(bytes, bytes.length)\n\n  override def writeTo(output: CodedOutputStream): Unit = {\n    output.writeRawBytes(bytes)\n  }\n\n  override def getSerializedSize: Int = bytes.length\n\n  override def getParserForType: Parser[? <: MessageLite] = {\n    throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"Parsing is exercised through the builder\")\n  }\n\n  override def toByteString: ByteString = ByteString.copyFrom(bytes)\n\n  override def toByteArray: Array[Byte] = payload()\n\n  override def writeTo(output: OutputStream): Unit = {\n    output.write(bytes)\n  }\n\n  override def writeDelimitedTo(output: OutputStream): Unit = {\n    output.write(bytes.length)\n    output.write(bytes)\n  }\n\n  override def isInitialized: Boolean = true\n}\n\nfinal class SerializedFormModernLiteMessage(bytes: Array[Byte]) extends SerializedFormBaseLiteMessage(bytes) {\n  override def newBuilderForType(): MessageLite.Builder = new SerializedFormModernBuilder()\n\n  override def toBuilder(): MessageLite.Builder = new SerializedFormModernBuilder().mergeFrom(payload())\n\n  override def getDefaultInstanceForType: MessageLite = SerializedFormModernLiteMessage.DEFAULT_INSTANCE\n}\n\nobject SerializedFormModernLiteMessage {\n  @static val DEFAULT_INSTANCE: SerializedFormModernLiteMessage = new SerializedFormModernLiteMessage(Array.emptyByteArray)\n}\n\nfinal class SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage(bytes: Array[Byte]) extends SerializedFormBaseLiteMessage(bytes) {\n  override def newBuilderForType(): MessageLite.Builder = new SerializedFormLegacyBuilder()\n\n  override def toBuilder(): MessageLite.Builder = new SerializedFormLegacyBuilder().mergeFrom(payload())\n\n  override def getDefaultInstanceForType: MessageLite = SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage.defaultInstance\n}\n\nobject SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage {\n  @static val defaultInstance: SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage = new SerializedFormLegacyLiteMessage(Array.emptyByteArray)\n}\n\nabstract class SerializedFormBaseBuilder extends MessageLite.Builder {\n  private var bytes: Array[Byte] = Array.emptyByteArray\n\n  override def clear(): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    bytes = Array.emptyByteArray\n    this\n  }\n\n  override def build(): MessageLite = buildPartial()\n\n  override def clone(): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    val cloned: SerializedFormBaseBuilder = newBuilder()\n    cloned.bytes = Arrays.copyOf(bytes, bytes.length)\n    cloned\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(input: CodedInputStream): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    mergeFrom(input, ExtensionRegistryLite.getEmptyRegistry)\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(input: CodedInputStream, extensionRegistry: ExtensionRegistryLite): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    val output: ByteArrayOutputStream = new ByteArrayOutputStream()\n    while (!input.isAtEnd) {\n      output.write(input.readRawByte().toInt)\n    }\n    mergeFrom(output.toByteArray)\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(data: ByteString): MessageLite.Builder = mergeFrom(data.toByteArray)\n\n  override def mergeFrom(data: ByteString, extensionRegistry: ExtensionRegistryLite): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    mergeFrom(data)\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(data: Array[Byte]): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    bytes = Arrays.copyOf(data, data.length)\n    this\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(data: Array[Byte], offset: Int, length: Int): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    bytes = Arrays.copyOfRange(data, offset, offset + length)\n    this\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(data: Array[Byte], extensionRegistry: ExtensionRegistryLite): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    mergeFrom(data)\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(\n    data: Array[Byte],\n    offset: Int,\n    length: Int,\n    extensionRegistry: ExtensionRegistryLite\n  ): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    mergeFrom(data, offset, length)\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(input: InputStream): MessageLite.Builder = mergeFrom(input.readAllBytes())\n\n  override def mergeFrom(input: InputStream, extensionRegistry: ExtensionRegistryLite): MessageLite.Builder = {\n    mergeFrom(input)\n  }\n\n  override def mergeFrom(message: MessageLite): MessageLite.Builder = mergeFrom(message.toByteArray)\n\n  override def mergeDelimitedFrom(input: InputStream): Boolean = {\n    val length: Int = input.read()\n    if (length < 0) {\n      false\n    } else {\n      mergeFrom(input.readNBytes(length))\n      true\n    }\n  }\n\n  override def mergeDelimitedFrom(input: InputStream, extensionRegistry: ExtensionRegistryLite): Boolean = {\n    mergeDelimitedFrom(input)\n  }\n\n  override def isInitialized: Boolean = true\n\n  override def getDefaultInstanceForType: Messa